arttime faculty member for usc’s graduate taxation program for approximately ten years and is a member of the board of advisors for the leventhal school of accounting at usc and the graduate tax program at loyola law school other professional affiliations include the american institute of certified public accountants the california society of certified public accountants the american bar association and the state bar of california phil also serves on the boards of ascent capital group nasdaq and several nonprofit organizations including harvardwestlake school the music center leadership council and the angeleno and los angeles chapters of wpoeducationjd loyola law school in los angelesms business taxation university of southern california summa cum laudebs business administration university of southern california summa cum laudebloomberg bna tax management portfolios tm real estate leases coauthor standing orders all bloomberg bna treatises are available on standing order which ensures you will always receive the most current edition of the book or supplement of the title you have ordered from bloomberg bna’s book division as soon as a new supplement or edition is published usually annually for a title you’ve previously purchased and requested to be placed on standing order we’ll ship it to you to review for  days without any obligation during this period you can either a honor the invoice and receive a  discount in addition to any other discounts you may qualify for off the thencurrent price of the update plus shipping and handling or b return the books in which case your invoice will be cancelled upon receipt of the books call us for a prepaid ups label for your return it’s as simple and easy as that most importantly standing orders mean you will never have to worry about the timeliness of the information you’re relying on and you may discontinue standing orders at any time by contacting us at  or by sending an email to booksbnacom put me on standing order at a  d